//   - Tempo chain state tracked internally (was external input param only)
//   - BB efficiency metric added (CORD input)
//   - bbDebtForgivenessPerRound reads from config constant (was magic 50)
//   - predatorCardAdapter now routes through generateBB() — single source of truth
//   - Per-round history ring buffer for analytics
